                  , about the hour of seven on the night of the <rs id="t18140112-46-cd245" type="crimeDate">25th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140112-46-off244 t18140112-46-cd245"></join>, and stealing therein a pocket-book, value 6 d. three three-shilling bank tokens, and thirty-five shillings in monies numbered
            </rs>, the property of 
